1
00:00:07,674 --> 00:00:08,996
It's time for you to go.

2
00:00:08,996 --> 00:00:10,090
What?

3
00:00:11,071 --> 00:00:13,500
October 6th, 2030.

4
00:00:13,501 --> 00:00:15,235
By the order of the underworld...

5
00:00:15,235 --> 00:00:16,610
Hey!

6
00:00:16,610 --> 00:00:18,405
What the hell are you doing?

7
00:00:23,197 --> 00:00:25,325
I'm fucked...

8
00:00:29,163 --> 00:00:33,809
[Samdocheon Grim Reaper Academy]

9
00:00:33,810 --> 00:00:36,770
How long are you gonna do nothing but study for this exam?

10
00:00:36,770 --> 00:00:39,230
This is your eighth try. Eighth.

11
00:00:39,230 --> 00:00:42,049
At this rate, when are you ever passing the Grim Reaper exam?

12
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:45,138
Look at this.

13
00:00:45,138 --> 00:00:47,554
Your strokes are still a mess.

14
00:00:47,554 --> 00:00:49,899
Ugh... I don't know, this is too hard

15
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:51,460
I quit...

16
00:00:51,460 --> 00:00:52,833
Pick up the pen.

17
00:00:52,833 --> 00:00:54,833
Nope.

18
00:00:56,053 --> 00:00:57,518
Let's do a test.

19
00:00:57,519 --> 00:00:58,679
What, another Chinese character...

20
00:00:58,679 --> 00:01:00,679
Not that.

21
00:01:00,679 --> 00:01:02,490
Really?

22
00:01:02,490 --> 00:01:04,231
What kind of test?

23
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:12,125
Here, take this.

24
00:01:16,530 --> 00:01:18,300
You're going down to the human world

25
00:01:18,300 --> 00:01:20,160
and bringing back a dead soul.

26
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:21,630
The human world?

27
00:01:21,630 --> 00:01:25,920
Inside that envelope is a human name
written in Chinese characters.

28
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:29,549
Bring back the human that matches
that name to the underworld.

29
00:01:30,690 --> 00:01:32,292
That's it?

30
00:01:32,292 --> 00:01:33,890
Yep.

31
00:01:33,890 --> 00:01:36,150
But there is one thing
you absolutely need to remember.

32
00:01:36,150 --> 00:01:37,660
What's that?

33
00:01:37,660 --> 00:01:41,014
You have to finish the mission
and get back within five days.

34
00:01:41,775 --> 00:01:44,071
Otherwise you'll be stuck there.

35
00:01:44,740 --> 00:01:45,919
But...

36
00:01:45,919 --> 00:01:47,710
if I pass this test,

37
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:49,816
I officially become a Grim Reaper, right?

38
00:01:49,816 --> 00:01:51,524
Of course.

39
00:01:52,017 --> 00:01:53,893
And...

40
00:01:53,893 --> 00:01:56,955
never develop feelings for a human.

41
00:01:57,360 --> 00:02:00,140
Love between a Grim Reaper
and a human is forbidden,

42
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:04,184
and if you break that rule,
the consequences are brutal.

43
00:02:05,385 --> 00:02:08,360
Me? Falling in love with someone...?

44
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,730
Don't worry

45
00:02:09,730 --> 00:02:11,691
I'll bring them back in no time.

46
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:13,790
If that's everything,

47
00:02:13,790 --> 00:02:15,929
I can head out now, right?

48
00:02:21,730 --> 00:02:23,463
Then...

49
00:02:23,463 --> 00:02:25,825
I'm off!

50
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:28,475
Wait!

51
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,650
Why do I need this?

52
00:02:39,650 --> 00:02:41,370
I won't need it in the human world.

53
00:02:41,370 --> 00:02:44,100
You do use that in the human world.

54
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:48,495
It's the only way to contact the underworld
from the underworld, the living from the living,

55
00:02:48,496 --> 00:02:52,386
and sometimes even the underworld
from the human world.

56
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:55,775
If something seriously unexpected happens,

57
00:02:55,990 --> 00:02:57,931
use this to call me.

58
00:02:58,118 --> 00:03:00,305
Yeah, yeah, got it.

59
00:03:00,306 --> 00:03:02,282
Alright, I'm heading out now.

60
00:03:14,101 --> 00:03:16,533
I finally made it to the human world...

61
00:03:16,540 --> 00:03:18,324
And if I nail this mission,

62
00:03:18,325 --> 00:03:21,275
I officially become a full-fledged Grim Reaper, right?

63
00:03:39,070 --> 00:03:40,220
Whoa.

64
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:43,289
So trees are actually a real thing here

65
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:46,960
I've been locked in a room studying
Chinese characters my whole life,

66
00:03:47,401 --> 00:03:48,955
and these humans...

67
00:03:49,203 --> 00:03:51,846
they've got it pretty nice, huh?

68
00:04:03,277 --> 00:04:05,432
Chinese Character Club?

69
00:04:05,433 --> 00:04:07,774
They study Chinese characters here too?

70
00:04:16,291 --> 00:04:18,692
Oh no... are you okay?

71
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:22,722
What do I do?

72
00:04:23,350 --> 00:04:26,573
Uh... that's not good...

73
00:04:36,450 --> 00:04:39,220
Um... are you alright?

74
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:41,354
Uh... yeah...

75
00:04:41,355 --> 00:04:42,749
I'm sorry too

76
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:44,830
I didn't realize you were next to me.

77
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:47,821
Was this... something really important?

78
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:50,757
It was important, but...

79
00:04:51,144 --> 00:04:53,360
it should be okay.

80
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:04,604
I'm Kim Jaehyun, a sophomore in Visual Design.

81
00:05:04,971 --> 00:05:06,065
Oh!

82
00:05:06,065 --> 00:05:07,814
I'm...

83
00:05:08,333 --> 00:05:13,818
Uh... I'm Kang Jihan,
a freshman in the same department...

84
00:05:15,275 --> 00:05:17,083
Visual Design too?

85
00:05:17,083 --> 00:05:19,083
Didn't see that coming.

86
00:05:20,288 --> 00:05:21,890
Man...

87
00:05:21,890 --> 00:05:24,511
What a terrible first impression to make on my junior.

88
00:05:24,511 --> 00:05:26,400
Huh? No, no, it's okay

89
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,350
I was at fault too...

90
00:05:28,350 --> 00:05:30,977
I'll buy you a meal sometime.

91
00:05:31,537 --> 00:05:34,400
Freshman year's rough, isn't it?

92
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:37,370
If you ever need help, just let me know.

93
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:40,127
Oh!

94
00:05:44,698 --> 00:05:47,794
This is my number.

95
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:49,923
As for yours...

96
00:05:49,923 --> 00:05:52,099
that might be a little too much right now.

97
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:54,594
Just call me anytime, okay?

98
00:05:54,594 --> 00:05:56,594
Ah... okay.

99
00:06:00,832 --> 00:06:03,222
I've got class soon, so I should get going.

100
00:06:04,182 --> 00:06:06,091
Text me!

101
00:06:08,738 --> 00:06:11,171
Why is he so damn nice?

102
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:18,218
Ah... more importantly, what do I do about this?

103
00:06:22,533 --> 00:06:25,672
Ah... I'm seriously screwed...

104
00:06:34,615 --> 00:06:36,503
Kang Jihan?

105
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:51,687
What the... what kind of Chinese character is this...?

106
00:06:56,463 --> 00:06:58,712
I should've paid more attention in Chinese class...

107
00:07:08,976 --> 00:07:11,604
Let's find him and get back out of here.

108
00:07:11,605 --> 00:07:14,730
You can do this... you can do this, Kang Jihan!

109
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:24,044
Not this one...

110
00:07:25,819 --> 00:07:27,781
Not this either...

111
00:07:30,053 --> 00:07:31,718
Where the hell is this guy?

112
00:07:31,719 --> 00:07:34,839
My eyeballs are gonna fall out at this rate.

113
00:07:35,303 --> 00:07:38,338
Could they at least tell me what he looks like?

114
00:07:39,798 --> 00:07:42,325
This damn underworld system, seriously...

115
00:07:43,917 --> 00:07:45,545
Ah, shit!

116
00:07:45,546 --> 00:07:46,292
I'm so sorry...

117
00:07:46,292 --> 00:07:48,060
I asked my friend to toss me a snack,

118
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:50,356
and he threw it like an idiot...

119
00:07:51,930 --> 00:07:53,640
Um...

120
00:07:55,402 --> 00:07:57,204
No, it's okay.

121
00:07:57,204 --> 00:07:58,824
Stuff happens.

122
00:07:58,825 --> 00:08:01,027
Ah, right... well then...

123
00:08:03,483 --> 00:08:04,279
Huh?

124
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,019
That's...

125
00:08:06,019 --> 00:08:07,694
Excuse me!

126
00:08:15,749 --> 00:08:17,123
It's time for you to go.

127
00:08:17,123 --> 00:08:18,524
What?

128
00:08:19,210 --> 00:08:21,600
October 6th, 2030.

129
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,316
By the order of the underworld...

130
00:08:23,316 --> 00:08:24,684
Hey!

131
00:08:24,684 --> 00:08:26,684
What the hell are you doing?

132
00:08:39,406 --> 00:08:41,427
I'm fucked...

133
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:45,700
"Fix the Error!"

134
00:09:05,900 --> 00:09:07,700
("Underworld Notice" Please report immediately
upon locating the wanted fugitive)
